## Data Source Map (where each piece of content lives)

| Content | Source | How it reaches page |
|---------|--------|---------------------|
| Content stats (Pan-African/End-to-End/6/3) | `content_stats` table (DB) | `GET /api/content/stats` → `useContentStats()` → fallback `FALLBACK_STATS` |
| Methodology steps | `methodology_steps` table (DB) | `GET /api/content/methodology` → `useMethodologySteps()` → fallback `FALLBACK_STEPS` |
| Site settings (hero, branding, about, etc.) | `site_settings` table (DB) | `GET /api/content/settings/:key` → `useSiteSetting(key)` → deepMerge with page DEFAULTS |
| Projects | `projects` table (DB) | `GET /api/projects` → `useProjects()` |
| Services | `services` table (DB) | `GET /api/services` → `useServices()` |
| Testimonials | `testimonials` table (DB) | `GET /api/content/testimonials` |
| FAQs | `faqs` table (DB) | `GET /api/content/faqs` |
| Static copy fallbacks | In-component DEFAULTS / FALLBACK_* constants | Used when API data is loading or empty |
